net.floodlightcontroller.util

类 OFMessageUtils.OFMessageIgnoreXid

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.util.OFMessageUtils.OFMessageIgnoreXid
  • 封闭类:
    OFMessageUtils

    public static class OFMessageUtils.OFMessageIgnoreXid
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple class to streamline the use of OFMessage's equalsIgnoreXid() and hashCodeIgnoreXid() functions. Use this class to wrap OFMessages prior to inserting them in containers where lookup or equality checks should not include the XID. See OFMessageDamper as an example where it's used to help cache OFMessages.
